metadata.name: PANDA MERGE ES
metadata.description:
Hello. Welcome to a web3 adventure. This is an NFT f*ucking full of Easter Eggs.

You can have each word of a seed phrase to access a wallet with 0.1 eth and 2 NFTs from the PFP Supply Co collection.  
To find them, you need to search a lot. Maybe you can find some clues on Twitter, things in its own contract, or even in a song!

Good luck.

As a gift I will give you the first clue:  
https://soundcloud.com/siryus/rqn1koogzgls
